    {
      "@id": "http://lod.footlight.io/resource/6855a4b5aef58a0064a486ed",
      "@type": "Person",
      "description": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Logan Staats is a Canadian singer-songwriter and musician. Staats achieved mainstream success throughout 2018, and in 2019, off of his win on the first season of CTV's The Launch. He is best known for his single, \"The Lucky Ones\" which hit number one on the Canadian iTunes chart right after its release. He is also known for his part in the 2017 Canadian made documentary, When They Awake which celebrates Indigenous artists and their communities."
      },
